D. Acquisition Strategy
DAI is developed and implemented using an evolutionary/incremental strategy including major annual software releases to accommodate upgrades as required by
changes to the Department’s BEA including new laws, regulations and policies as governed by its Functional Sponsor.

 DAI Increments 1 and 2 are in sustainment. When Increment 3, Release 1 went live in October 2018, it subsumed Increment 2; therefore, only one DAI production
 baseline exists at any point in time.




