and has a clean audit history. With an integrated accountability, utilization, maintenance, and warehouse capability, DPAS provides the Department an enterprise
solution for asset management.$$, $$The DPAS system provides accountability and management functionality of General Equipment, Real Property and Internal Use Software, to the Department. The
