A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
The Defense Property Accountability System (DPAS) provides the Department an asset accountability system which is fully compliant with financial reporting regulations
and has a clean audit history. With an integrated accountability, utilization, maintenance, and warehouse capability, DPAS provides the Department an enterprise
solution for asset management.

