                                                                                                                   FY 2025   FY 2026    Base       OOC          Total
plans, coordinate near term modernization plans, and coordinate shore and shipboard installations to ensure
support prior to deployments, resolve schedule issues and establish priorities. Major issues identified at each
NCMC are reported to a joint FFC/CPF flag/SES panel.

