D. Acquisition Strategy
The WGC program acquisition strategy takes advantage of 10 U.S.C 2302 Middle Tier of Acquisition (MTA) and was designated a MTA for Rapid Prototyping in May
2019 and completed in May 2024. The program was designated a MTA for Rapid Fielding in May 2024. The overarching strategy consists of four phases: Phase I: Risk
Reduction Prototyping (FY 2019 - FY 2020); Phase II: Integrated Prototyping (FY 2020 - FY 2022); Phase III: Baselining (FY 2023 - FY 2024) and Production; Phase IV:
Sustainment/Operations.




